726464f-a.text:
Cypress Hills Street (foreground), between Fresh Pond Road (left) and 64th Street (right). This is a set of two views showing the rear of two homes facing on Fresh Pond Road. At the extremes of view No. 1 are the homes of Edsall and Henry W. Meyer respectively. The home of Henry W. Meyer (right) is now the 116th Precinct Police and Station house.
March 1923.
View 2: 1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
